casebody.data:
Michael Ramon OCHOA, petitioner,
v.
Erin RUBIN, aka Erin Rubin Ochoa. No. 14-6408. Supreme Court of the United States Nov. 3, 2014.

Opinion

Motion of petitioner for leave to proceed in forma pauperis denied, and petition for writ of certiorari to the Superior Court of Pennsylvania, Pittsburgh Office, dismissed. See Rule 39.8.
